--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	INSTALLATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Python packages are available from
https://github.com/emsrc/timbl-tools/wiki/Python-Packages
For installation instruction see the file INSTALL.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    DOCUMENTATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

All executable scripts are self-documenting: use the '-h' options. 

Other documentation, including API reference information, is available in the
doc directory.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    KNOWN ISSUES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* TimblServer process is not always killed 


